{"tid":403361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣好抗拒食苦瓜？","createTime":"2017-09-17T06:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T16:05:53.000Z","uid":122071,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2029e0bda78ecb8bb81ff70c3d5f1ec6786637","tid":403361,"uid":122071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:55:29.000Z","msg":"我細細個就好唔中意食瓜，我好中意食老麥既雙層芝士孖堡既包但會走青瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n屋企人就好中意食苦瓜，成日整苦瓜湯，苦瓜炒蛋，苦瓜炒肉片等等～我好憎食，我屋企人就會成日整千奇百趣既配搭比我食，希望我接受到，但都仲未撈到一件苦瓜菜式我接受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我嗅到苦瓜既味就好抗拒，好唔中意嗅同食。<br />\n<br />\n到大個左都會嘗試下食瓜類，依家仲唔洗走青瓜，但依然都接受唔到苦瓜味道，係咪要歷練多幾個人生先懂得欣賞苦瓜既甜？<br />\n<br />\n有無人建議下整苦瓜既菜式既配搭，可以比我參考？揀飲擇食真係唔岩，但我真係好唔中意苦瓜。"},{"pid":"c481fdd285662bf2d7785d9c518c3d715fd986c4","tid":403361,"uid":92325,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"細個好憎<br />\n大左勁中意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煮得好食是唔苦的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeeb33c5d1ba7880c337995cf7c803cc0662fb36","tid":403361,"uid":90863,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:56:51.000Z","msg":"幾鍾意食<br />\n苦瓜排骨湯<br />\n<br />\n可能因為我老母可以整到佢唔苦"},{"pid":"b1559a553d32b9a284cb012a162a46dbe47f9e48","tid":403361,"uid":128413,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"苦瓜炒苦瓜都唔錯架"},{"pid":"df0ba558f47d50ebe56bf64695730d91b42f4e99","tid":403361,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:57:53.000Z","msg":"你前世應該係比瓜揼死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e8f58306c6d41d0524cdcc0019cafb0172d739","tid":403361,"uid":122071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個好憎<br />\n大左勁中意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煮得好食是唔苦的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n甜左都係仲覺得係苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe8f77a24ea9ae28f6347962014f71c539dc869","tid":403361,"uid":121546,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"到你大個D自己買送既時候就唔會有偏食既問題架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為正常人唔會買自己唔鐘意食既野"},{"pid":"739a3a1c4ed21583f7bb30d1b76e1af4a169605f","tid":403361,"uid":141985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:01:47.000Z","msg":"苦瓜豆豉鯪魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 苦瓜有分幾種 有一種短身大粒凸嘅好似唔苦"},{"pid":"a9801a22603350a8acea34b3fb81046b47ffa321","tid":403361,"uid":122071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你前世應該係比瓜揼死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係，仲要棺材有苦瓜陪葬，仲討厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927897c33e2a9cb8c17f54f22b4577b3f60a0f7e","tid":403361,"uid":64512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:04:49.000Z","msg":"好撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一黎佢樣衰 二黎佢苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f7ddb878cb55614c1a0f4ecb5145e6524b8334","tid":403361,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"吃得苦中苦, 方為人上人"},{"pid":"a272d3d52f5b9d68f45b7afd59177d8543cb1b01","tid":403361,"uid":70205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"真想不到當初我們也討厭吃苦瓜"},{"pid":"376534885c14d91a89c54e48c5f6e6ebbec82d46","tid":403361,"uid":122071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到你大個D自己買送既時候就唔會有偏食既問題架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為正常人唔會買自己唔鐘意食既野</blockquote><br />\n呢個真，依家都唔會去選擇買"},{"pid":"5e6257e0c91c71c48e8a83ee3aff6f5065400347","tid":403361,"uid":122071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一黎佢樣衰 二黎佢苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩，仲有臭苦瓜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632072136e055355e17f621a3eadf24b7a54e634","tid":403361,"uid":23560,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:10:15.000Z","msg":"啲苦瓜買雷公鑿嗰隻<br />\n然後切好搵啲粗鹽先乸一乸佢<br />\n佢會出啲黃色水<br />\n出水之後再沖一次水洗一洗先煮<br />\n就會無咗苦味<br />\n用蒜頭炒熟就好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ba88a55ef054b696ecc9eb7b35c8a1000ac260","tid":403361,"uid":122071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>苦瓜豆豉鯪魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 苦瓜有分幾種 有一種短身大粒凸嘅好似唔苦</blockquote><br />\n原來有分，點分架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727e66ded9639d80b4ac9174779195caabad7663","tid":403361,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"用鹽淹過就唔苦嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6360cbddef03ca78b3ad45a0f4de3af61b57e221","tid":403361,"uid":49963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:15:10.000Z","msg":"真想不出當初我們也討厭吃苦瓜"},{"pid":"3e9d037b2944b9ca85b734a4d84fdcba4385ba3c","tid":403361,"uid":72445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"半生瓜"},{"pid":"c9b4a71cbaf4e8b71dadb0e89226afc8a90d66aa","tid":403361,"uid":121131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真想不到當初我們也討厭吃苦瓜</blockquote><br />\nX2"},{"pi