:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:30:14.000Z","msg":"雷公鑿好吃d，長身果隻唔好吃"},{"pid":"89bae7148f6363e34aa98c9176e6277f40de6398","tid":403361,"uid":51134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:34:48.000Z","msg":"真想不到當初我們也討厭吃苦瓜"},{"pid":"42844c7d92871ece13fac3e76e6fc07c85f5d196","tid":403361,"uid":122071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雷公鑿好吃d，長身果隻唔好吃</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知苦瓜有分咁多類"},{"pid":"54b12fe3025b4538a3610d5d6efdc3ba2efdb25a","tid":403361,"uid":140411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:39:32.000Z","msg":"苦過後更加清"},{"pid":"428cdf066a4ad65314a20ab16c6129cdfc4c77e6","tid":403361,"uid":131146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:40:07.000Z","msg":"樓主未吃過苦"},{"pid":"a73d31a47cd14d774e03733061e478a07a9a9e42","tid":403361,"uid":6427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"釀苦瓜幾好味 有肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3af272802df7086add2ad486f7d09e729e5658","tid":403361,"uid":37343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"大過咗乜都食，燈籠椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />青椒<br />\n<br />\n建議十幾歲細路乜都試吓就最好。"},{"pid":"1e3473cfa64003b415db5a5f7f451d59d6c6c8e6","tid":403361,"uid":52793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"以前會好憎食，嫌苦<br />\n宜家就唔抗拒。<br />\n其實同隊啤酒，甚至食煙差唔多，因為生活更苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b50a585c39d5ad85aff7c07cc9031c5a556e693","tid":403361,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:13:08.000Z","msg":"細個好憎食苦瓜<br />\n但而家逐漸愛上咗個種澀澀地嘅味<br />\n好想返返去唔食苦瓜既時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca62286b2418e17ed278b4e275e6724e37cdc62c","tid":403361,"uid":136590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:39:24.000Z","msg":"樓主唔鍾意食苦瓜嘅原因好簡單<br />\n就係你嘅人生未夠苦 帶唔出苦瓜本身嘅甘味"},{"pid":"9b8fde4d202b7e84273660c8bbe26ca23815dc28","tid":403361,"uid":12820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"我都唔鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都諗唔明 人鍾意食好味嘅嘢好正常<br />\n點解有好嘢唔食要去食啲苦嘅嘢<br />\n明白有好多人鍾意食苦瓜 但點解每次同人講我唔鍾意食苦瓜都畀人話乜話物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔食都有罪咁"},{"pid":"7a466313c9ba12861b14daef41c21bc444b6c139","tid":403361,"uid":122071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主未吃過苦</blockquote><br />\n吃過人生苦，但味覺苦唔受得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa34da0d28ee50fe44161443eb7bfd488527aff7","tid":403361,"uid":122071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都唔鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都諗唔明 人鍾意食好味嘅嘢好正常<br />\n點解有好嘢唔食要去食啲苦嘅嘢<br />\n明白有好多人鍾意食苦瓜 但點解每次同人講我唔鍾意食苦瓜都畀人話乜話物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔食都有罪咁</blockquote><br />\n真，味覺同人生係唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我味覺抵不住苦瓜味"},{"pid":"eb3348019ce7570d0554ab6ab807c843e5df27ae","tid":403361,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細個好憎<br />\n大左勁中意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煮得好食是唔苦的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你一樣，我覺得苦瓜呢家野可能年紀越大就自自然接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要浸多幾年歷練先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能真係要<img src=\"